# UI copy capitalization (Vyooo)

User-facing **labels** use **Title Case**: capitalize the first letter of each word.

## Applies to

- App bar titles
- Settings / list tile labels
- Button labels (primary, secondary, dialog actions)
- Section headers and tab names
- Short status chips (e.g. `Coming Soon`)

## Does not apply to

- Long body copy, subtitles, and snackbar sentences (sentence case)
- User-generated content
- Brand tokens: `Vyooo`, `VR`, acronyms (`OTP`, `4K`)

## Source of truth

Shared settings/account strings: `lib/core/strings/app_strings.dart`. Reuse constants when adding duplicate labels.

## Examples

| Use | Style |
|-----|-------|
| Settings tile | `Personal Information` |
| Button | `Log Out`, `Sign In` |
| Section | `Creator Tools` |
| Snackbar | `Sign in to follow people.` (sentence) |
